WEBVTT

00:15.348 --> 00:16.558
<i>Griselda.</i>

00:17.350 --> 00:19.019
<i>We need to talk.</i>

00:19.644 --> 00:20.979
<i>Papo got Amilcar's territories.</i>

00:21.062 --> 00:23.314
<i>He doesn't want to be
in business with you.</i>

00:23.398 --> 00:26.317
<i>He already made a deal with Rafa.
I'm going with him.</i>

00:26.401 --> 00:29.863
<i>I told you I was gonna
fuck you back one way or another.</i>

00:35.827 --> 00:37.537
<i>I brought your dealers.</i>

00:37.620 --> 00:38.663
<i>You got nothing to give.</i>

00:38.747 --> 00:40.832
<i>Why didn't you
take the buyout?</i>

00:40.915 --> 00:42.876
<i>The door is that way, bitch.</i>

01:02.145 --> 01:03.730
<i>The truth is...</i>

01:05.607 --> 01:07.442
<i>you scare me more than they do.</i>

01:12.947 --> 01:15.617
<i>Some boats
are too rickety to make the trip.</i>

01:15.700 --> 01:17.869
<i>The State Department
has warned the boat operators</i>

01:17.952 --> 01:19.996
<i>they could be arrested
and given stiff fines.</i>

01:20.080 --> 01:21.706
<i>But still it goes on this morning.</i>

01:21.790 --> 01:25.668
<i>A ragtag armada of boats
traveling between Miami and Cuba</i>

01:25.752 --> 01:27.170
<i>to bring out the Cubans who say</i>

01:27.253 --> 01:30.507
<i>they can no longer stand
to live under Communist rule.</i>

01:30.590 --> 01:34.761
For too long, gangs of
drug dealers have held our city hostage,

01:34.844 --> 01:37.388
which is why today,
I'd like to announce the formation

01:37.472 --> 01:40.141
of a new federally-mandated CENTAC unit.

01:40.850 --> 01:43.895
This task force includes
local and federal agents

01:43.978 --> 01:46.564
and will be led by Detective Raul Diaz.

01:48.691 --> 01:50.151
Congratulations.

01:50.235 --> 01:52.195
Thank you very much. Jim, how are you?

01:59.786 --> 02:02.080
This is the house I told you about.

02:02.163 --> 02:05.583
We'll be here a few days
until I'm done fixing some things.

02:05.667 --> 02:07.961
-  What things?
-  Things.

02:08.628 --> 02:12.423
-  Think I saw an alligator.
-  What's with the new security?

02:12.507 --> 02:14.342
Just a precaution.

02:25.478 --> 02:26.938
This is Rigo.

02:27.021 --> 02:29.607
He and his cousins
came over on those boats

02:29.691 --> 02:31.484
from Cuba we saw on the news, Ozzy.

02:31.568 --> 02:33.278
They call us "Marielitos."

02:38.032 --> 02:39.033
Put them on.

02:39.117 --> 02:39.951
Thank you.

02:40.577 --> 02:42.912
Help unload the car.

02:43.663 --> 02:44.998
I gotta make a call.

02:49.335 --> 02:50.587
Rigo thinks your mom's a saint

02:50.670 --> 02:53.172
'cause she gave jobs
to him and his cousin.

02:59.804 --> 03:02.265
<i>Look at you. You're drunk too.</i>

03:02.348 --> 03:03.266
<i>Come on. Let's go.</i>

03:09.147 --> 03:09.981
Hello.

03:10.064 --> 03:11.357
<i>How's it going?</i>

03:11.900 --> 03:13.818
Just doing a deep clean.

03:13.902 --> 03:16.154
You mean getting high in the backyard?

03:16.237 --> 03:20.116
We need a "vacation," too.

03:20.199 --> 03:21.159
And?

03:21.868 --> 03:22.827
It happen yet?

03:23.995 --> 03:25.538
I haven't given the order yet.

03:26.915 --> 03:28.207
Listen to me.

03:28.791 --> 03:31.294
Back in the day,
when a man treated us like shit,

03:31.377 --> 03:33.463
all we could do was knee him in the nuts.

03:34.005 --> 03:35.465
Now you got the means,

03:35.548 --> 03:37.967
do not feel bad taking back what's yours.

03:38.718 --> 03:39.761
<i>What's going on?</i>

03:39.844 --> 03:42.597
She's gonna fuck up
the assholes who stole her territory.

03:42.680 --> 03:45.016
Fuck yeah, Godmother!

03:46.559 --> 03:48.770
Clean the house at some point, okay?

03:48.853 --> 03:50.730
Aye, aye, captain.

03:51.397 --> 03:52.232
<i>Good luck.</i>

04:09.874 --> 04:10.708
<i>Hello.</i>

04:12.585 --> 04:13.461
We're here.

04:15.213 --> 04:16.130
Get going.

04:25.890 --> 04:27.058
Who are these people?

04:27.141 --> 04:28.977
Must be the house owners.

04:29.060 --> 04:32.105
Rigo. Chucho.
Dario's en route. You should go.

04:41.656 --> 04:42.991
Where they going?

04:43.700 --> 04:45.660
Nowhere. Go get settled.

05:28.244 --> 05:30.413
- That him?
-  Mm-hmm.

05:33.333 --> 05:35.001
Party's on.

06:04.739 --> 06:06.240
No one comes out alive.

06:15.124 --> 06:16.584
You see what Castro's doing?

06:17.251 --> 06:19.003
Already enough Cubans in this town.

06:19.837 --> 06:22.090
They're like fucking roaches.

06:22.173 --> 06:24.050
- You want a beer, Dad?

06:24.133 --> 06:25.051
