said the hitter had nice tats too.

17:15.325 --> 17:16.744
Could be another Marielito.

17:20.372 --> 17:21.206
Yeah.

17:22.332 --> 17:25.544
Which one out of the hundred thousand
that have come here so far?

17:47.566 --> 17:49.068
