-  We're here.

17:53.363 --> 17:54.323
We're here.

18:02.039 --> 18:03.832
This is my aunt, Rigo's mother.

18:04.541 --> 18:06.418
I need to speak to Ms. Blanco.

18:07.377 --> 18:08.212
Please.

18:12.216 --> 18:14.301
I came here from Cuba years ago.

18:16.011 --> 18:19.848
But my son was in prison
for something he did very young.

18:21.433 --> 18:24.394
I waited and waited
until Castro let him come.

18:25.312 --> 18:26.522
And now

18:27.439 --> 18:29.024
I'll never see him again.

18:30.776 --> 18:31.985
I have sons.

18:33.237 --> 18:34.905
I can't imagine.

18:36.532 --> 18:41.411
Rigo said you're a mother to three boys,
but also to all who work for you.

18:42.621 --> 18:44.748
He said people call you the Godmother.

18:47.042 --> 18:49.962
So perhaps you know the answer.

18:52.172 --> 18:53.006
Tell me.

18:53.090 --> 18:55.134
They cut off my boy's head.

18:57.719 --> 19:00.639
Do you think he can still go to heaven?

19:04.393 --> 19:05.769
Yes, of course.

19:09.022 --> 19:10.983
Your son Rigo died because of me.

19:13.944 --> 19:16.405
You don't know how sorry I am.

19:16.488 --> 19:19.366
There's no one we can trust here.

19:21.827 --> 19:26.039
The police, the people in charge,
they're no different than those in Cuba.

19:26.123 --> 19:27.624
So many of these boys came here,

19:29.459 --> 19:31.086
but have nothing.

19:31.170 --> 19:33.005
Nothing to do.

19:33.088 --> 19:34.381
Nothing to believe in.

19:36.008 --> 19:37.134
You gave him that.

19:38.385 --> 19:43.557
If Rigo's brothers ever make it here,

19:43.640 --> 19:46.268
I hope they can work for you too.

19:49.563 --> 19:50.606
Let's go.

19:50.689 --> 19:51.815
Thank you.

19:54.234 --> 19:55.527
Esmerelda, wait.

19:57.362 --> 19:59.406
What if I can fix it for you?

20:00.949 --> 20:03.619
Make these men pay for what they did

20:03.702 --> 20:06.288
and give you the money
to bring your other sons here.

20:10.417 --> 20:11.501
You would do that?

20:13.378 --> 20:14.671
For you, anything.

20:23.597 --> 20:24.556
Hello.

20:24.640 --> 20:27.684
