but I don't speak Spanish.

24:30.510 --> 24:31.928
Sir.

24:32.012 --> 24:33.180
Did you see something?

24:34.389 --> 24:37.392
There were three,
but I didn't see their faces.

24:37.475 --> 24:39.895
I only know that one of them was a woman.

24:46.234 --> 24:47.319
There were more,

24:47.402 --> 24:49.821
but this was all that would fit
in the trucks.

24:51.323 --> 24:52.449
I got this for you.

24:56.077 --> 24:58.830
For them, you may want to wear it.

25:10.675 --> 25:12.636
Thank you all for coming.

25:14.846 --> 25:16.640
I'm Griselda Blanco.

25:24.022 --> 25:26.233
We both have the same problem.

25:26.816 --> 25:31.655
Every room I walk into, I'm just a woman.

25:31.738 --> 25:37.327
Every room you walk into,
you're just a Marielito.

25:39.913 --> 25:41.456
When people look at you,

25:42.123 --> 25:45.126
they only see your tattoos
and that you don't speak English.

25:45.752 --> 25:49.714
They think, "How can I use them?"

25:49.798 --> 25:51.549
"How can I abuse them?"

25:51.633 --> 25:55.303
The only way to get what we want

25:55.387 --> 25:59.349
